HOW IT'S MADE
-----------------------

- Download Zig from official site. (No installation required). Use the last Release, not latest 'master'.

- Get the Release of 'PZRE' from https://codeberg.org/jetill/pzre, 
  place to "pzre" subfolder. (Remove old files).

- If required, the "src\main.zig" file can be edited in Visual Studio Code or any editor.

- To build, execute:

    > build.cmd

  (If "zig.exe" is not in PATH, "build.cmd" can be adjusted to include the path).

  It will create the "zig-out\bin\ZigPzreWorker.exe" file.

- Commit the changes (including "ZigPzreWorker.exe") to Git.

- Build the main Visual Studio solution.

